{"tid":2032061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟出左聲明回應國安法   有外國手足打左去屌柒佢地","createTime":"2020-05-23T22:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:58:29.000Z","uid":256407,"like":559,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1636b57c313693b4527b8e637f5c19ac6ee6f8","tid":2032061,"uid":256407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:30:31.000Z","msg":"歐盟前日出左聲明回應國安法<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/05/22/declaration-by-the-high-representative-on-behalf-of-the-european-union-on-the-announcement-by-china-s-national-people-s-congress-spokesperson-regarding-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2Fdeclaration-by-the-high-representative-on-behalf-of-the-european-union-on-the-announcement-by-china-s-national-people-s-congress-spokesperson-regarding-hong-kong%2F&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=0856a036\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/05/22/declaration-by-the-high-representative-on-behalf-of-the-european-union-on-the-announcement-by-china-s-national-people-s-congress-spokesperson-regarding-hong-kong/</a>)，但內容廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同無出聲唔知有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有外國手足嬲到即刻打俾EU呢位仁兄問佢歐洲做乜鳩個腦坐住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪武肺完都唔知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AZCueT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AZCueT.jpg&h=b5a0a80a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n又真係打通左，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錄音係度</span></span>：<a href=\"https://we.tl/t-fTr7AJHG7q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-fTr7AJHG7q&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b79665a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-fTr7AJHG7q</a><br />\n手足如果有野關於呢份<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">零分重作</span></span>既聲明有疑問，可以隨時搵佢地傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7956c55fa82463fb85b55a6eeedbc087d5050e08","tid":2032061,"uid":308595,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:31:49.000Z","msg":"多謝外國手捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaecc5c265ec2e2be7af213f3ef582bebe4c9be9","tid":2032061,"uid":41423,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:33:51.000Z","msg":"I thank you for nothing,thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6dc1586894ad183ae7a65ae758acf809fc469e","tid":2032061,"uid":88982,"like":95,"dislike":4,"score":91,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"Thank you for nothing.<br />\n擺明心裡面爆緊粗但係又要扮君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72166252c53b5fd3e8fd96d6717cbc46dda8fd5","tid":2032061,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:16:03.000Z","msg":"Lmlm"},{"pid":"2562235f3bda2400d9250707f72ef53d78b51b31","tid":2032061,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb55d46f9204382bc8cd07a6aad7dbfcff744ed8","tid":2032061,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d42b9083da73efac9336cf2e36c2cc5f15646f","tid":2032061,"uid":38953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:48:03.000